# Code Ownership for Ubik Enterprise
#
# This file defines code ownership for the monorepo.
# Review requests are automatically sent to code owners when PRs touch their areas.
#
# Syntax: <path-pattern> <@owner> <@owner> ...
# The last matching pattern takes precedence.
#
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# =============================================================================
# Default Owners
# =============================================================================

# Default owners for everything in the repo
* @rastrigin-org/ubik-maintainers

# =============================================================================
# Services
# =============================================================================

